actions.message:
```
General Commands


!Help                   Lists available commands
!SendEmbed              Sends an embed message
!UserInfo               Displays the user's information
!ChannelInfo            Displays the channel's information
!RoleInfo [role-name]   Displays info for the role
!Slap [@user]           Slaps the mentioned user
!FlipCoin               Returns "Heads" or "Tails"
!GenNumber [min] [max]  Returns a random number
!Gold                   Display's the user's gold
!Gamble                 The user randomly gains or loses some gold
!ban                    Bans a user (personally made by lapis)
!memes                  Gives some memes to cheer ya up (made by lapis)
!game                   (bot owner only cmd)
!8ball                   Gives a random scentence
!warn                    (warns people)
!blacklist                Stops a user from messaging and deletes it


Ticket Commands
!new
!close
```

{
  "name": "Steal",
  "permissions": "NONE",
  "restriction": "1",
  "_id": "JNbud",
  "actions": [
    {
      "member": "1",
      "varName": "",
      "dataName": "gold",
      "defaultVal": "0",
      "storage": "1",
      "varName2": "myGold",
      "name": "Store Member Data"
    },
    {
      "member": "0",
      "varName": "",
      "dataName": "gold",
      "defaultVal": "0",
      "storage": "1",
      "varName2": "myGold",
      "name": "Store Member Data"
    },
    {
      "info": "0",
      "infoIndex": "1",
      "storage": "1",
      "varName": "mem",
      "name": "Store Command Params"
    },
    {
      "storage": "1",
      "varName": "mem",
      "comparison": "5",
      "value": "@",
      "iftrue": "0",
      "iftrueVal": "",
      "iffalse": "2",
      "iffalseVal": "11",
      "name": "Check Variable"
    },
    {
      "member": "0",
      "varName": "",
      "dataName": "gold",
      "comparison": "3",
      "value": "100",
      "iftrue": "2",
      "iftrueVal": "14",
      "iffalse": "0",
      "iffalseVal": "",
      "name": "Check Member Data"
    },
    {
      "storage": "1",
      "varName": "gold",
      "min": "1",
      "max": "5000",
      "name": "Generate Random Number"
    },
    {
      "member": "0",
      "varName": "",
      "dataName": "gold",
      "comparison": "3",
      "value": "${tempVars(\"gold\")}",
      "iftrue": "2",
      "iftrueVal": "16",
      "iffalse": "0",
      "iffalseVal": "",
      "name": "Check Member Data"
    },
    {
      "channel": "0",
      "varName": "",
      "message": "${member}, you stole **${tempVars(\"gold\")}** from ${tempVars(\"mem\")}!",
      "storage": "0",
      "varName2": "",
      "name": "Send Message"
    },
    {
      "member": "0",
      "varName": "",
      "dataName": "gold",
      "changeType": "1",
      "value": "-${tempVars(\"gold\")}",
      "name": "Control Member Data"
    },
    {
      "member": "1",
      "varName": "",
      "dataName": "gold",
      "changeType": "1",
      "value": "${+tempVars(\"gold\")}",
      "name": "Control Member Data"

    {
      "name": "End Action Sequence"
    },
    {
      "channel": "0",
      "varName": "",
      "message": "${member}, **you must mention a member to steal from!\nIts kinda pointless to steal from no one...**",
      "storage": "0",
      "varName2": "",
      "name": "Send Message"
    },
    {
      "name": "End Action Sequence"
    },
    {
      "channel": "0",
      "varName": "",
      "message": "${member}, ${tempVars(\"mem\")} **doesnt have enough budget.**",
      "storage": "0",
      "varName2": "",
      "name": "Send Message"
    },
    {
      "name": "End Action Sequence"
    },
    {
      "channel": "0",
      "varName": "",
      "message": "${member}, **the user you are trying to steal from is too poor..**",
      "storage": "0",
      "varName2": "",
      "name": "Send Message"
    }
  ],
  "_timeRestriction": 600
}

      "iftrue": "2",
      "iftrueVal": "18",
      "iffalse": "0",
      "iffalseVal": "",
      "name": "Check Member Data"
    },
    {
      "member": "1",

    {
      "storage": "1",
      "varName": "chance",
      "min": "1",
      "max": "100",
      "name": "Generate Random Number"
    },
    {
      "behavior": "0",
      "interpretation": "0",
      "code": "parseInt(tempVars('input')) * 1.75",
      "storage": "1",
      "varName": "won",
      "name": "Run Script"
    },
    {
      "storage": "1",
      "varName": "chance",
      "comparison": "3",
      "value": "41",
      "iftrue": "2",
      "iftrueVal": "13",
      "iffalse": "2",
      "iffalseVal": "15",
      "name": "Check Variable"
    },
    {
      "name": "End Action Sequence"
    },
    {
      "channel": "0",
      "varName": "",
      "message": "${member}, you lost **${tempVars(\"input\").toLocaleString('en')}** GCA Coins...",
      "storage": "0",
      "varName2": "",
      "iffalse": "0",
      "iffalseVal": "",
      "name": "Send Message"
    },
    {
      "name": "End Action Sequence"
    },
    {
      "member": "1",
      "varName": "",
      "dataName": "gold",
      "changeType": "1",
      "value": "${1.75*tempVars(\"input\")}",
      "name": "Control Member Data"
    },
    {
      "channel": "0",
      "varName": "",
      "message": "${member}, you won. You received **${tempVars(\"won\").toLocaleString('en')}** GCA Coins!",
      "storage": "0",
      "varName2": "",
      "iffalse": "0",
      "iffalseVal": "",
      "name": "Send Message"
    },
    {
      "name": "End Action Sequence"
    },
    {
      "channel": "0",

      "message": "${member}, **you dont have enough budget to do this..**",
      "storage": "0",
      "varName2": "",
      "name": "Send Message"
    },
    {
      "name": "End Action Sequence"
    },
    {
      "channel": "0",
      "varName": "",
      "message": "${member}, **make sure to enter an ammount greater then 100!**",
      "storage": "0",
      "varName2": "",
      "name": "Send Message"
    },
    {
      "name": "End Action Sequence"
    },
    {
      "storage": "1",
      "varName": "LowerChance",
      "min": "1",
      "max": "100",
      "name": "Generate Random Number"
    },
    {
      "storage": "1",

      "iftrueVal": "24",
